# Integrations and config

- This repo references bizprofile.net (main site, forms, XHR), static.bizprofile.net (PDFs), CDN (Fancybox, jQuery), and Google Fonts. No REST client, Stripe, or API SDK in-repo. See ./docs/04-integrations-and-infra.md.
- Do not add new external services, env-based config, or API clients without tech-lead agreement. Forms and link-more XHR target the same origin; do not assume backend APIs or persistence not present in the repo.
- When adding or changing links to external hosts, keep usage consistent with current patterns (e.g. rel="nofollow" on PDF links). New routes or form actions require backend support; do not point forms or critical links to unimplemented URLs.
